Articles.Content:
I purchased KSP in December of 2016, and have been playing it off and on ever since. However, due to a couple of rules I imposed on myself, as well as a lack of patience, I have never been interplanetary. Well, earlier this week one of my friends found that out, and began pestering me to go interplanetary. I gave in, and the result is what you see here. 

I present to you

The oh so creatively named Duna I mission, my first interplanetary mission.
